Patricia MORGAN, n/k/a Patricia Beckman, joined by her husband, Richard Beckman, Appellants, v. Thomas L. PASSMORE and Mary C. Passmore, his wife, Appellees. No. 69-699. District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. March 24, 1970. Rehearing Denied April 13, 1970.

March 24, 1970.

Frank E. Freeman, Michelle Friedlander & Paul Marcus, Miami, for appellants. Milton R. Wasman, Miami, for appellees. Before PEARSON, C. J., and CHARLES CARROLL and BARKDULL, JJ. PER CURIAM.

Affirmed. See Cohen v. Cohen, Fla. 1954, 70 So.2d 362, 363; Althouse v. State Farm Fire & Casualty Company, Fla.App. 1966, 183 So.2d 859; Brown v. Householdor, Fla.App.1961, 134 So.2d 801.
